or pick up in person from: Dynamic Concepts, Inc., Room 2229, Interstate Commerce Commission Building, 1201 Constitution
Avenue, N.W., Washington, DC 20423. Telephone (202) 289-4357/4359. [Assistance for the hearing impaired
is available through TDD services: (202) 927-5721.] 



We reaffirm our initial finding that the exemption will not significantly affect either the quality of the human environment
or the conservation of energy resources. 

