(2) Claims not over $2,500 generated by AAFES activities will be transmitted to the Army-Air Force Exchange Service,
OSC-FA-CLAIMS, P.O. Box 650405, Dallas, TX 76265-0405.

(3) Claims over $100 generated by other nonappropriated fund activities will be transmitted to The Army Central Insurance
